==English==

===Etymology===
See [[organ]]
===Adjective===
'''organic'''
# pertaining to, derived from, like, of the nature of, an organ (in any sense)
# in [[chemistry]], relating to the [[compound]]s of [[carbon]], relating to [[natural]] [[product]]s
# of [[food]] or food products, grown in an [[environment]] free from [[artificial]] [[agro-chemical]]s, and possibly certified organic by a regulatory body.

